mphasizes the importance of Latin, despite the lack of surviving manuscripts, and teaching and learning in a highly decentralized environment. Within this context, it explores how medieval grammatical education was adapted for bilingual clerical education, which in turn helped create a separate and fully vernacularized grammatical discourse.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Apr 2021) 0aEducationzIcelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 4aAlphabetisierung. 4aAltnordisch. 4aAusbildung. 4aIsland / Geschichte. 4aMittelalter. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aMedieval Education.  aMedieval Icelandic History.  aMedieval Literacy.  aOld Norse.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2021z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z978311075377608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishz978311075408708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021z97831107538510 cEPUBz97815015144320 cprintz978150151855340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150151418040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501514180423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781501514180.jpg  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Ebook Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  a978-3-11-075385-1  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075408-7  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA